headline: Lennar (NYSE:LEN) Unveils Roselyn: A Vibrant 55+ Community With Homes From US$300,000s
summary: Lennar (NYSE:LEN) recently opened a new community, Roselyn, in Lancaster County, targeting homebuyers aged 55 and older. This expansion into the active adult market is indicative of its continued growth strategy. Though its share price remained flat with a 0.68% movement last month, the broader market rose 1.2% over the same period.
